quran[399]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"Iye adati, “Kodi inu Atumwi uthenga wanu ndi wotani?”"
  51,32,"Iwo adati, “Ife tatumidwa kwa anthu ochimwa.”"
  51,33,“Kuti tigwetse pa iwo miyala yamakande.”
  51,34,“Idakonzedwa ndi Ambuye wako kudza kwa anthu oswa malamulo.”
  51,35,Ndipo Ife tidatulutsa anthu okhulupirira amene adali momwemo
  51,36,Koma sitidapezemo mabanja a Chisilamu kupatula banja limodzi lokha basi
  51,37,Ndipo Ife tidasiyamo chizindikiro kwa iwo amene amaopa chilango chowawa
  51,38,Ndi mwa Mose. Pamene tidamutumiza kwa Farawo ndi zizindikiro zooneka
  51,39,"Koma Farawo adakana pamodzi ndi mafumu ake nati, “Ndiwe munthu wamatsenga kapena munthu wa misala.”"
  51,40,Motero tidamugwira pamodzi ndi gulu la asirikali ake ndi kuwamiza onse m’nyanja pamene iye ndiye adali wolakwa
  51,41,Ndipo mwa a Aad pamene tidawatumizira mphepo yoononga
  51,42,Imene sidasiye chilichonse chimene idalimbana nacho kupatula kuchiononga ndi kuchisandutsa phulusa
  51,43,"Ndipo mwa anthu a Thamoud. Pamene adauzidwa kuti, “Basangalalani kanthawi kochepa.”"
  51,44,"Koma iwo adaphwanya lamulo la Ambuye wawo mwamwano, kotero mabingu adawaononga iwo ali kuona"
  51,45,Kotero iwo adalibe mphamvu zodzuka kapena zodzitetezera
  51,46,Ndi anthu a Nowa iwo asanadze. Ndithudi iwo adali anthu oswa malamulo
  51,47,"Ife tidakonza kumwamba mwamphamvu ndiponso mwaluso. Ndipo, ndithudi, ndife amene timapanga kukula kwa mlengalenga"
  51,48,"Ndipo dziko, tidamwaza. Kodi ndife omwaza bwino bwanji"
  51,49,Ndipo zonse zimene tidalenga tidazilenga ziwiriziwiri kuti mukhoza kukumbukira
  51,50,Kotero thawirani kwa Mulungu. Ndithudi Ine ndine mchenjezi wooneka kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,51,Ndipo musapange fano kukhala lopembedzedwa pamodzi ndi Mulungu. Ndithudi ine ndine mchenjezi wooneka kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,52,"Chimodzimodzi palibe Mtumwi amene adadza kwa anthu amene sadamunenere mawu ofanana monga akuti: “Wamatsenga kapena munthu wopenga!”"
  51,53,"Kodi uwu ndi mwambo umene akhala ali kusiyirana wina ndi mnzake? Iyayi, iwo ndi anthu amene ali kuswa malamulo mopyola muyeso"
  51,54,Kotero uwaleke chifukwa iwe ulibe mlandu
  51,55,Ndipo kumbutsa chifukwa chikumbutso chimathandiza anthu okhulupirira
  51,56,Ndipo Ine ndidalenga majini ndi anthu kuti azindipembedza Ine
  51,57,Ine sindiwapempha chakudya ndipo sindiwafunsa kuti azindidyetsa Ine
  51,58,"Ndithudi ndi Mulungu yekha amene amapereka chakudya chonse, Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi wolimba kwambiri"
  51,59,"Ndithudi anthu onse olakwa adzalandira gawo longa limene anzawo olakwa akale adalandira, kotero asandifunse Ine kuchita mofulumira"
  51,60,Kotero tsoka kwa onse osakhulupirira kuchokera ku tsiku lomwe iwo alonjezedwa
  52,1,Ndi pali phiri
  52,2,Ndi pali Buku lolemekezeka
  52,3,Lili chikopa chosapinda
  52,4,Ndi pali Bait – Ul-Ma’mur (Nyumba imene ili kumwamba yolingana ndi Kaaba imene ili ku Makka ndipo imaonedwa ndi angelo pafupipafupi)
  52,5,Ndi pali denga lonyamuka
  52,6,Ndi pali nyanja yodzadzidwa ndi madzi ambiri
  52,7,Ndithudi chilango cha Ambuye wako chidzakwaniritsidwa
  52,8,Palibe wina amene angachiletse
  52,9,"Pa tsiku limeneli, kumwamba kudzagwedezeka koopsa"
  52,10,Ndipo mapiri adzagudubuzika osakhalanso china chake
  52,11,"Kotero tsoka, patsiku limeneli kwa anthu abodza"
  52,12,Amene amatangwanika ndi mabodza
  52,13,Patsikuli iwo adzatengedwa ndi kuponyedwa mwamphamvu ku moto wa ku Gahena
  52,14,Uwu ndi moto umene mumati ndi bodza
  52,15,Kodi amenewa ndi matsenga kapena simutha kuona
  52,16,"Lawani kutentha kwake ndipo kaya inu mupirira kapena ayi, kwa inu ndi chimodzimodzi; inu muli kulandira malipiro a ntchito zomwe mumachita"
  52,17,"Ndithudi iwo amene ali olungama, adzakhala m’minda mwamtendere"
  52,18,Kusangalala chifukwa cha zimene Ambuye wawo wawapatsa ndipo Ambuye wawo wawapulumutsa ku chilango cha ku Gahena
  52,19,“Idyani ndi kumwa mwachisangalalo chifukwa cha ntchito zanu zabwino zomwe mudachita.”
  52,20,"Iwo adzakhala pa mipando yawofowofo, yoikidwa m’mizere. Ndipo Ife tidzawakwatitsa kwa amene ali ndi maso akuluakulu ndi okongola"
  52,21,"Ndipo iwo amene amakhulupirira ndipo ana awo amawatsatira m’chipembedzo, oterewa tidzawakumaniza ndi mabanja awo ndipo Ife sitidzawachotsera chilichonse cha malipiro a ntchito zawo zabwino. Munthu aliyense adzafunsidwa malinga ndi ntchito zake"
  52,22,Ndipo tidzawapatsa zipatso ndi nyama zimene iwo afuna
  52,23,Kumeneko iwo adzapatsana wina ndi mnzake chikho chimene mulibe zinthu zopanda pake kapena uchimo
  52,24,Iwo adzazunguliridwa ndi kutchingidwa bwino ndi anyamata awoawo amene adzawatumizira ngati kuti iwo anali ndolo zobisika
  52,25,Ndipo iwo adzafunsana wina ndi mnzake ndi kuyankhulitsana
  52,26,"Iwo adzati, “Kale ife tidali a mantha ndi mabanja athu.”"
  52,27,“Koma Mulungu wationetsera chisomo chake ndipo watipulumutsa ife ku chilango cha kumoto.”
  52,28,“Ndithudi ife tinali kumupempha Iye yekha. Ndithudi Iye ndiye Mwini chifundo ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha.”
  52,29,"Motero pitiriza kukumbutsa ndi kulalikira. Chifukwa cha chisomo cha Ambuye wako, iwe si ndiwe munthu wonyenga kapena wamisala"
  52,30,"Kapena iwo amati, “Ndi Mlakatuli, ife tili kuyembekezera kuti choipa chidze pa iye.”"
  52,31,"Nena, “Yembekezerani! Nanenso ndili mmodzi wa oyembekezera.”"
  52,32,Kodi ndi maganizo awo amene ali kumawauza izi kapena iwo ndi anthu amene amaswa malamulo mosadodoma
  52,33,"Kodi kapena iwo amati, “Iye wapeka yekha uthengawu? Iyayi! iwo alibe chikhulupiriro.”"
  52,34,Alekeni nawo abweretse mawu olingana ndi awa ngati iwo ali kunena zoona
  52,35,Kodi iwo adalengedwa popanda china chake kapena iwo ndiwo a Namalenga
  52,36,Kapena ndiwo amene adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi? Iyayi! iwo alibe chikhulupiriro chokhazikika
  52,37,Kodi ndiwo amene amasunga chuma cha Ambuye wako? Kapena iwo ndiwo a nkhanza amene ali ndi ulamuliro wonena chilichonse chimene afuna
  52,38,Kodi kapena iwo ali ndi njira yomvetsera zomwe zinali kunenedwa? Motero mulekeni kazitape wawo kuti apereke umboni wokwanira
  52,39,Kodi kapena Iye ali ndi ana aakazi okha pamene inuyo muli ndi ana aamuna
  52,40,Kodi kapena iwe uli kuwafunsa malipiro kotero kuti iwo apanikizidwa kwambiri ndi ngongole
  52,41,Kodi kapena ali ndi zobisika ndipo amazilemba
  52,42,Kodi kapena ali kukonza chiwembu? Koma iwo amene sakhulupirira ndiwo amene ali ndi chiwembu
  52,43,Kodi kapena ali ndi mulungu wina kupatula Mulungu weniweni? Mulungu alemekezeke kuposa zimene iwo amamufanizira nazo
  52,44,"Ndipo iwo akadaona gawo lina la kumwamba lili kugwa pansi ndipo iwo akadati, “Ndi mitambo youndana.”"
  52,45,Motero alekeni mpaka pamene iwo akumana ndi tsiku lawo limene iwo adzakomoka ndi mantha
  52,46,Tsiku limene chiwembu sichidzawathandiza china chilichonse ndipo chithandizo sichidzaperekedwa kwa iwo
  52,47,"Ndipo, ndithudi, onse amene amachita zoipa, kuli chilango china pa chilango ichi koma ambiri a iwo sadziwa"
  52,48,"Motero pirira podikira chiweruzo cha Ambuye wako, chifukwa ndithudi iwe uli kusamalidwa ndi Ife ndipo lemekeza Ambuye wako pamene uuka ku tulo"
  52,49,"Nthawi ya usiku, lemekeza ulemerero wake ndi pa nthawi yolowa nyenyezi"
  53,1,Ndi pali nyenyezi pamene ili kulowa
  53,2,M’bale wanu sadasochere kapena kuti ndi wolakwa
  53,3,Ndipo iye sayankhula zofuna zake
  53,4,Icho ndi chochita kuuzidwa kwa iye
  53,5,Iye adaphunzitsidwa ndi Iye amene ali ndi mphamvu
  53,6,"Wopanda chilema chilichonse, kotero adadzuka ndi kukhala wokhazikika"
  53,7,Pamene iye anali patali kwambiri mu mlengalenga
  53,8,Ndipo adasendera ndi kudza pafupi
  53,9,Ndipo adali pa mtunda wolingana kuponya mipaliro iwiri kapena kucheperapo
  53,10,Motero Iye adaulula Uthenga kwa kapolo wake kudzera mwa Gabriyele
  53,11,Mtima wake wa Mtumwi siudaname ponena zimene iye adaona
  53,12,Kodi inu mudzatsutsana naye pa zimene iye adaona
  53,13,Ndithudi iye adamuona iye pamene anali kutsika kachiwiri
  53,14,Pafupi ndi mtengo wa Sidrah
  53,15,Pafupi pake pali munda womwe ndi malo opumirako
  53,16,Ndipo chimene chimaphimba chidakuta mtengo wa Sidrah
  53,17,Maso ake sadayang’ane kumbali kapena kupyola muyeso
  53,18,Ndithudi iye adaona zizindikiro zazikulu kwambiri za Ambuye wake
  53,19,Kodi inu maganiza za Lat ndi Uzza
  53,20,Ndi Manat wachitatu wamkazi
  53,21,Kwa inu amuna ndipo kwa Iye akazi
  53,22,Ndithudi kumeneku ndiko kugawa kosalungama
  53,23,"Awa ndi mayina chabe amene inu mwapeka, inu ndi atate anu, amene Mulungu sadakulamuleni ndi pang’ono pomwe. Iwo amangotsatira nkhani zakumva chabe zimene mitima yawo imafuna pamene, ndithudi, kwadza kale kwa iwo ulangizi wochokera kwa Ambuye wawo"
  53,24,Kodi munthu angapeze zonse zimene amafuna
  53,25,Koma Mulungu ndiye Mwini moyo umene uli nkudza ndi moyo wakale
  53,26,Ndipo kuli angelo ambiri amene ali kumwamba amene kukhala pakati kwawo sikudzathandiza chilichonse kupatula pokhapo pamene Mulungu apereka chilolezo kwa amene Iye wamufuna ndi kukondweretsedwa naye
  53,27,"Ndithudi iwo amene sakhulupirira za m’moyo umene uli nkudza, amatcha angelo ndi mayina achikazi"
  53,28,"Pamene iwo sadziwa chilichonse cha izo. Iwo satsatira china chilichonse koma nkhani zabodza ndipo, ndithudi, nkhani zabodza si mlowam’malo wa choonadi"
  53,29,Motero mupewe wina aliyense amene salabadira chikumbutso chathu ndipo safuna china chilichonse koma moyo wa padziko lino lapansi
  53,30,Uko ndiko kuchuluka kwa nzeru zawo. Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndiye amadziwa bwino onse amene amasochera ku njira yoyenera ndipo amadziwa kwambiri iye amene amatsata njira yoyenera
  53,31,"Ndipo Mulungu ndiye mwini wake wa chilichonse chimene chili kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, ndipo akhoza kulanga onse amene amachita zoipa molingana ndi ntchito zawo ndiponso kuti akhoza kulipira onse amene amachita zabwino ndi mphotho yabwino kwambiri"
  53,32,"Iwo amene amapewa machimo a akuluakulu ndi chigololo kupatula machimo a ang’onoang’ono, ndithudi, Ambuye wako ndi Mwini chikhululukiro. Iye amakudziwani bwino pamene amakulengani kuchokera ku dothi ndi pamene mukutidwa m’mimba mwa amayi anu. Motero musadziyeretse nokha. Al Najm\t567 Iye amadziwa bwino kwambiri aliyense amene amalewa zoipa"
  53,33,Kodi iwe wamuona amene amabwerera m’mbuyo
  53,34,Amene adapereka pang’ono ndipo anasiya kupereka
  53,35,Kodi iye amadziwa za zinthu zobisika kuti akhoza kuziona
  53,36,Kodi kapena iye sadauzidwe za mawu amene ali m’mabuku a Mose
  53,37,Ndiponso za Abrahamu amene adakwaniritsa malamulo
  53,38,Kuti palibe munthu amene adzasenza katundu wa mnzake
  53,39,Ndipo kuti munthu sadzapeza chilichonse kupatula chimene wachigwirira ntchito
  53,40,Ndipo kuti ntchito zake zidzaoneka
  53,41,Pamenepo iye adzalipidwa malipiro ake oyenera
  53,42,Ndipo kuti kwa Ambuye wanu ndi kumene nonse mudzapita
  53,43,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amawachititsa anthu kuseka ndi kuwaliritsa
  53,44,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amapereka imfa ndi moyo
  53,45,"Ndiponso kuti Iye adalenga zinthu ziwiriziwiri, chachimuna ndi chachikazi"
  53,46,Kuchokera ku madontho a umuna umene umatuluka
  53,47,Ndipo kuti kwa Iye kuli chilengedwe chachiwiri
  53,48,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amapereka chuma ndi chisangalalo
  53,49,Ndipo kuti Iye ndiye Ambuye wa nyenyezi yamphamvu yotchedwa Sirius
  53,50,Kuti ndiye amene adaononga anthu akale a mphamvu kwambiri a mtundu wa a Aad kale
  53,51,Ndi anthu a mtundu wa a Thamoud. Ndipo Iye sadasiye wina aliyense
  53,52,Ndi anthu a Nowa amakedzana ndithudi iwo adali osalungama ndi oswa malamulo mwamwano
  53,53,Ndipo iye adaononga mizinda yomwe idali yogonjetsedwa
  53,54,Kotero iwo adawavundikira nd chimene chidawavundikira
  53,55,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wako zimene udzazikayikira
  53,56,Uyu ndi mchenjezi wotsatizana ndi achenjezi a makedzana
  53,57,Tsiku louka kwa akufa lili pafupi
  53,58,Palibe wina kupatula Mulungu amene akhoza kulipherera
  53,59,Kodi inu mulikudabwa pa zimene zili kulakatulidwa
  53,60,Ndipo inu muli kuseka m’malo mwakulira
  53,61,Ndi kumapitirizabe kuchita zinthu zopanda pake
  53,62,Motero gunditsani nkhope zanu pansi ndipo pembedzani Mulungu mmodzi yekha
  54,1,Ola lachiweruzo lili pafupi ndipo mwezi wagawanika pakati
  54,2,"Koma iwo akaona chozizwitsa, sakhulupirira ndipo amati, “Ichi sichina ayi koma matsenga ozama.”"
  54,3,Iwo amakana choonadi koma amatsatira zilakolako zawo. Koma chinthu chilichonse chili ndi kumaliza kwake
  54,4,Ndithudi uthenga waperekedwa kale kwa iwo umene uli ndi chenjezo
  54,5,Wodzadzidwa ndi nzeru koma machenjezo ake sawathandiza iwo china chilichonse
  54,6,"Kotero iwe, asiye okha. Patsiku limene woitana adzawaitana kudza ku chinthu choopsa"
  54,7,"Iwo adzadza kumeneko ndi nkhope zogwa pansi, kuchokera kumanda awo monga dzombe louluka ponseponse"
  54,8,"Adzadza mofulumira kwa oitana anthu osakhulupirira adzati, “Ili ndi tsiku lovuta kwambiri.”"
  54,9,"Asanadze iwo, anthu a Nowa adakana kapolo wathu ndipo adati, “Uyu ndi munthu wamisala.” Ndipo iwo adamuthamangitsa iye ndi kumunyoza kwambiri"
  54,10,"Ndipo iye adadandaula kwa Ambuye wake nati, “Ndagonjetsedwa kotero idzani kuti mundithandize.”"
  54,11,"Motero Ife tidatsekula makomo a kumwamba, ndipo mvula idagwa nthawi yomweyo"
  54,12,Ndipo tidatumphutsa a kasupe padziko lapansi kotero madzi onse adakumana monga mwa lamulo lathu
  54,13,Ndipo tidamunyamula iye m’chombo chopangidwandimatabwandichokhomedwandimisomali
  54,14,Chidanyamuka potsogozedwa ndi Ife. Mphotho kwa iye amene adakanidwa
  54,15,Ndithudi tidachisiya icho ngati chizindikiro koma kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,16,Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zalikulu bwanji
  54,17,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulidziwa ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,18,Anthu a Aad adakana. Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,19,Ndithudi Ife tidatumiza mphepo yamkhuntho pa tsiku latsoka losasimbika
  54,20,Kugwetsa anthu ngati kuti adali mathunthu a mitengo ya mgwalangwa yozulidwa
  54,21,Kodi chilango changa ndipo chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,22,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,23,Anthu a Thamoud adakana machenjezo
  54,24,"Iwo adati, “Munthu! Mmodzi yekha wochokera ku mtundu wathu kuti timutsatire? Ndithudi ife tikhala olakwa kwambiri ndiponso a misala.”"
  54,25,“Kodi ndiye kuti uthenga waperekedwa kwa iye yekha pakati pa ife tonse? Iyayi! Iye ndi wabodza ndi wodzikweza.”
  54,26,Mawa iwo adzadziwa kuti wabodza ndi wodzikweza ndani
  54,27,Ndithudi Ife titumiza ngamira yaikazi ngati mayesero kwa iwo. Motero iwe uwapenyetsetse ndipo ukhale wopirira
  54,28,Ndipo uwauze kuti azigawana madzi. Ndipo nthawi yomwera madzi idzakhazikitsidwa
  54,29,Ndipo iwo adaitana m’bale wawo ndipo iye adatulutsa lupanga ndi kuipha
  54,30,Kodi chilango changa ndi chenjezo langa zidali zoopsa bwanji
  54,31,Ndithudi tidawatumizira mfuwu umodzi ndipo onse adali ngati nkhuni zodula zimene munthu womanga mpanda amatola
  54,32,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Koma kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,33,Anthu a Loti adati chenjezo lathu ndi labodza
  54,34,Ndithudi Ife tidawatumizira mphepo yonyamula miyala kupatula a pa banja la Loti amene tidawapulumutsa mu ola lomaliza la usiku
  54,35,"Monga chisomo chochokera kwa Ife, motero ndi mmene timalipirira anthu oyamika"
  54,36,Ndithudi iye adawachenjeza za chilango chathu choopsa koma iwo adakana chenjezo lathu
  54,37,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iwo adafuna kuchititsa manyazi alendo ake. Motero Ife tidawachititsa khungu. Kotero inu lawani chilango changa ndi machenjezo anga"
  54,38,Ndithudi chilango chowawa chidadza pa iwo nthawi yam’mawa
  54,39,Kotero inu lawani chilango changa ndi machenjezo anga
  54,40,Ndithudi talipanga Buku la Korani kukhala losavuta kulizindikira ndi kulikumbukira. Kodi alipo ena amene adzachenjezedwa
  54,41,"Ndipo, ndithudi, machenjezo adadza kwa anthu a Farawo"
  54,42,Iwo adati machenjezo athu onse ndi abodza motero tidawaononga ndi chilango champhamvu yochuluka
  54,43,Kodi anthu anu osakhulupirira ndi abwino kuposa awa? Kapena inu muli ndi chitetezo mu m’mawu a Mulungu
  54,44,"Kodi kapena iwo amati, “Ife ndife ambiri ndipo tidzapambana?”"
  54,45,Tsopano magulu awo ali kupirikitsidwa ndipo iwo ali kuthawa
  54,46,"Iyayi, koma ola lachiweruzo ndi nthawi imene iwo adalonjezedwa ndipo ola limeneli lidzakhala loopsa kwambiri"
  54,47,Ndithudi anthu osakhulupirira ndi olakwa adzapsya
  54,48,"Tsiku limene iwo adzaduduluzidwa pa nkhope zawo kunka ku moto, (zidzanenedwa) “Lawani ululu wa ku Moto.”"
  54,49,Ndithudi tidalenga chilichonse molingana ndi muyeso wake
  54,50,Ndipo ulamuliro wathu ndi umodzi monga kuphenira kwa diso
  54,51,Ndithudi Ife tidaononga kale anthu onga inu koma kodi alipo amene anga chenjezedwe
  54,52,Ndipo zonse zimene adachita zidalembedwa
  54,53,Ndipo chilichonse chaching’ono ndi chachikulu chidalembedwa kale
  54,54,Ndithudi onse amene amalewa zoipa adzakhala m’kati mwa minda ndi mitsinje
  54,55,Ku Paradiso kufupi ndi Mfumu yamphamvu zonse
  55,1,Mwini Chifundo Chosatha
  55,2,Ndiye amene adamphunzitsa munthu Korani
  55,3,Ndiye amene adalenga munthu
  55,4,Wamuphunzitsa iye mawu anzeru
  55,5,Dzuwa ndi mwezi zimayenda m’misewu imene zinalamulidwa
  55,6,Zomera (kapena nyenyezi) ndi mitengo zonse zimagwada pomulambira Iye
  55,7,Iye adakweza kumwamba ndi kukhazikitsa muyeso
  55,8,Kuti inu musaphwanye muyeso
  55,9,Kotero khazikitsani muyeso wachilungamo ndipo musayese monyenga
  55,10,Ndiye amene adalenga dziko lapansi kuti zolengedwa zake zizikhalamo
  55,11,Mu ilo muli zipatso ndi mitengo ya tende yobereka phava la zipatso zambiri
  55,12,Ndi chimanga chimene masamba ndi mapesi ake amadyedwa ndi ziweto. Ndi mitengo yonunkhira
  55,13,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,14,Iye adalenga munthu kuchokera ku dothi monga dothi la mbiya
  55,15,Ndipo adalenga majini kuchokera kumoto wopanda utsi
  55,16,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,17,Ambuye wa kum’mawa kuwiri ndi Ambuye wa kumadzulo kuwiri
  55,18,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,19,Iye adasiya nyanja ziwiri kuti zikumane
  55,20,Pakati pawo pali malire amene madzi a uku sangathe kudutsa kupita uko
  55,21,"Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Rahman\t573 Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana"
  55,22,Mu zonse muli nkhombe zazikulu ndi zazing’ono
  55,23,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,24,"Ndipo zake ndi zombo zimene zimayenda pa nyanja, zazikulu ngati mapiri"
  55,25,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,26,Zonse zimene zili pa dziko zidzatha
  55,27,Ndipo nkhope ya Ambuye wako mu Ufumu ndi mu Ulemerero idzakhalabe mpaka kalekale
  55,28,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,29,Zonse zimene zimakhala kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi zimapempha kwa Iye. Tsiku lililonse Iye amakhala ndi chochita
  55,30,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,31,"Ife tidzadza kwa inu, Oh inu magulu awiri"
  55,32,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,33,"oh inu gulu la Majini ndi Anthu! Ngati muli ndi mphamvu zodutsa malire a kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, dutsani. Komatu inu simungadutse popanda chilolezo"
  55,34,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,35,Malawi a moto ndi utsi zidzaponyedwa kwa inu nonse awiri ndipo simudzatha kudziteteza nokha
  55,36,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,37,Ndi pamene thambo lidzagawanika pakati ndikukhala lofiira ngati mafuta osungunuka
  55,38,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,39,"Motero patsiku limeneli, sipadzakhala mafunso kuchokera kwa Munthu kapena Majini okhudza machimo awo"
  55,40,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,41,ochimwa adzadziwika ndi zizindikiro ndipo adzawagwira tsumba ndi pamapazi pawo
  55,42,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye
  55,43,Iyi ndi Gahena imene anthu ochimwa amati ndi bodza
  55,44,Iwo adzalowa m’kati mwake ndi m’kati mwa madzi ogaduka
  55,45,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,46,"Ndipo kwa iye amene aopa kuima pamaso pa Ambuye wawo, kudzakhala minda iwiri"
  55,47,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,48,Zokhala ndi mphanda zotambasuka
  55,49,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti zaAmbuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,50,Monse mudzakhala a kasupe awiri otumphuka
  55,51,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,52,M’menemu mudzakhala zipatso ziwiriziwiri za mitundumitundu
  55,53,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,54,Iwo adzagona pa makama amene nsalu yake ya m’kati idzakhala yasilika ndipo zipatso za m’minda iwiriyi zidzakhala pafupi pawo
  55,55,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,56,M’menemo mudzakhala wodzisunga ndi ogwetsa nkhope zawo pansi amene Munthu kapena Majini sadawakhudze
  55,57,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,58,olingana ndi miyala ya rubiya ndi ndolo
  55,59,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,60,Kodi dipo la ntchito yabwino lingakhale lina loposa ubwino
  55,61,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,62,Ndipo poonjezera pa minda iwiri pali minda ina iwiri
  55,63,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,64,Yooneka mobiriwira
  55,65,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,66,Monse mudzakhala a kasupe awiri otulutsa madzi ochuluka
  55,67,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,68,"Monse mudzakhala zipatso, tende ndi chimanga chachizungu"
  55,69,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,70,Mmenemo mudzakhala zinthu zokongola
  55,71,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,72,Angwiro ndi okhala m’mahema
  55,73,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,74,Amene Munthu kapena Majini sadawakhudze
  55,75,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,76,"Atakhala pa mipando yawofowofo, yobiriwira ndi mabedi okongola"
  55,77,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,78,"Lidalitsike dzina la Ambuye wako, Mwini ulemerero, chuma ndi ulemu"
  56,1,Pamene ola la chiweruzo lidza
  56,2,Ndipo palibe mzimu umene udzakana kudza kwake
  56,3,Kutsitsa gulu lina ndikukweza gulu linzake
  56,4,Pamene dziko lidzagwedezeka ndi chigwedezo choopsya
  56,5,Ndi pamene mapiri adzafumbutuka kukhala fumbi lokhalokha
  56,6,Motero iwo adzakhala fumbi louluzika paliponse
  56,7,Ndipo inu mudzagawidwa m’magulu atatu
  56,8,Iwo a ku dzanja la manja. Kodi a ku dzanja la manja adzakhala ndani
  56,9,Iwo akudzanja la mazere. Kodi akudzanja la mazere adzakhala ndani
  56,10,Ndipo gulu la iwo amene adzakhala kutsogolo m’chikhulupiriro adzakhala kutsogolo m’moyo umene uli nkudza
  56,11,Awa ndiwo amene adzakhala kufupi ndi Mulungu
  56,12,M’minda ya Paradiso
  56,13,Gulu lalikulu lidzachokera ku mibadwo ya kale
  56,14,Ndi gulu lochepa lidzachokera ku mibadwo ya m’mbuyo mwake
  56,15,Iwo adzakhala pa mipando yawofowofo yomatidwa golide ndi miyala ya mtengo wapatali
  56,16,Atakhala pa iyo ndi kumayang’anizana
  56,17,Iwo adzatumikiridwa ndi anyamata a muyaya
  56,18,"Ndi mabakuli, miphika ndi zikho za vinyo wabwino"
  56,19,Amene sadzawawitsa mitu yawo kapena kuwatopetsa
  56,20,Ndi zipatso zimene adzasankhepo
  56,21,Ndi nyama ya nkhuku imene angafune
  56,22,"Ndipo padzakhala anzawo okongola, a maso akulu ndi ochititsa kaso"
  56,23,Monga ndolo zosamalidwa bwino
  56,24,Malipiro a ntchito zimene adachita kale
  56,25,Palibe nkhani zopanda pake kapena zolaula zimene adzamva
  56,26,"Kupatula mawu akuti Mtendere, Mtendere"
  56,27,"Iwo a kudzanja lamanja, kodi akudzanja lamanja adzakhala ndani"
  56,28,Iwo adzakhala pakati pa m’mithunzi ya mitengo ya Sidrah
  56,29,Ndi m’mapata a nthochi zokhala ndi mikoko wina pamwamba pa unzake
  56,30,M’mithunzi yotambasuka
  56,31,Pambali pa madzi osefukira
  56,32,Ndi zipatso zochuluka
  56,33,Zimene nyengo yake sikutha ndipo kuchuluka kwake kudzakhalabe
  56,34,Ndi pa mipando yawofowofo yokwezedwa
  56,35,Ndithudi Ife tawalenga iwo mu chilengedwe cha padera
  56,36,Ndi kuwapanga kukhala a Namwali abwino
  56,37,A chikondi pa anzawo olingana nawo zaka
  56,38,A iwo amene adzakhala kudzanja lamanja
  56,39,"Gulu lochuluka lidzakhala lochokera ku mibadwo yoyamba, yakale"
  56,40,Gulu lochuluka lidzakhala lochokera ku mibadwo ya pambuyo pake
  56,41,Gulu la anthu a kudzanja lamanzere. Kodi anthu a kudzanja la manzere adzakhala otani
  56,42,M’katikati mwa malawi a moto ndi m’madzi ogaduka
  56,43,Ndi m’mithunzi ya utsi wakuda
  56,44,Yosazizira kapena yabwino
  56,45,Ndithudi iwo kale adali kukhala m’moyo wosavutika ndi opeza zinthu zambiri
  56,46,Ndipo adapitirira kuchita zoipa zikulu zikulu
  56,47,"Ndipo iwo anali kukonda kunena kuti: “Pamene ife tafa ndi kusanduka fumbi ndi mafupa, kodi tingadzaukitsidwenso?”"
  56,48,“Ndi makolo athu a nthawi ya makedzana?”
  56,49,"Nena: “Ndithudi onse oyambirira ndi otsiriza.”"
  56,50,“Ndithudi onse adzasonkhanitsidwa pamodzi pa tsiku lokhazikitsidwa.”
  56,51,“Kuphatikiza inu nonse amene muchimwa ndi kukana choonadi.”
  56,52,“Ndithudi inu mudzadya zipatso za mtengo wa Zaqqoom.”
  56,53,“Ndipo mudzakhutitsa mimba zanu ndi izo.”
  56,54,“Ndi kumwa madzi ogaduka.”
  56,55,“Ndi kumwa monga momwe ngamira yodwala ndi yaludzu imamwera.”
  56,56,Kumeneko ndiko kudzakhala kusangalala kwawo patsiku lachiweruzo
  56,57,Ndife amene tidakulengani inu nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simukhulupilira
  56,58,Ndiuzeni za umuna umene mumatulutsa
  56,59,Kodi ndinu amene mumaulenga kapena Ife ndife timaulenga
  56,60,Ife tidalamulira imfa kukhala pakati panu ndipo Ife sitingagonjetsedwe ayi
  56,61,Kukusinthani inu ndi kukulengani kukhala china chake chimene inu simuchidziwa
  56,62,Ndithudi inu mumadziwa za chilengedwe choyamba. Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simulabadira
  56,63,Kodi mudayamba mwaganiza za mbewu imene mumabzala
  56,64,Kodi ndinu amene mumaimeretsa kapena ndife amene timameretsa
  56,65,"Ngati titafuna, Ife tikadaiphwanya m’timagawomagawo touma ndipo inu mukadayamba kudandaula"
  56,66,Ndithudi ife tapatsidwa chingongole cholemera
  56,67,Iyayi. Koma tamanidwa
  56,68,Kodi inu mumawaona madzi amene mumamwa
  56,69,Kodi ndinu amene mumawagwetsa kuchokera ku mitambo kapena ndife
  56,70,Chikadakhala chifuniro chathu tikadawapanga iwo kukhala a mchere. Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simuthokoza
  56,71,Kodi inu mumaganizira za moto umene mumasonkha
  56,72,Kodi ndinu amene mumameretsa mtengo umene umayaka moto kapena ndife amene timaumeretsa
  56,73,Ife taupanga iwo kukhala chikumbutso ndi chinthu chothandiza anthu amene ali paulendo
  56,74,Kotero lemekezani dzina la Ambuye wanu Wamkulu
  56,75,Ndipo ndilumbira pali nyenyezi zimene zili kugwa
  56,76,Ndithudi ili ndi lonjezo lalikulu inu mukadadziwa
  56,77,Ndithudi ndi Buku lolemekezeka la Korani
  56,78,Limene lili m’Buku lotetezedwa
  56,79,Palibe amene adzalikhudza kupatula oyeretsedwa okha
  56,80,Chivumbulutso chochokera kwa Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  56,81,Kodi muli kunyozabe uthenga uwu
  56,82,Mmalo mothokoza chifukwa cha zinthu zimene amakupatsani inu mumamukana Iye
  56,83,Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani inu simuthandiza pamene mzimu wa munthu amene ali kufa ufika pa khosi pake
  56,84,"Pamene panthawiyo, inu mumangoyang’ana"
  56,85,Koma Ife tili pafupi ndi iye kuposa inu koma inu simutiona
  56,86,Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simutero ngati inu simudzaweruzidwa patsogolo pake
  56,87,Bwezerani mzimuwo ngati ndinu anthu a choonadi
  56,88,Ndipo ngati iye ndi mmodzi wa anthu amene ali kufupi ndi Mulungu
  56,89,Iye adzapeza mpumulo ndi chakudya ndi munda wa chisangalalo
  56,90,Ndipo ngati iye ndi wam’gulu la anthu akudzanja la manja
  56,91,Kotero kuli mtendere kwa iwo a kudzanja lamanja
  56,92,Ndipo ngati iye ndi mmodzi wa iwo okana choonadi ndi amene amalakwa
  56,93,Motero kulandiridwa kwake kudzakhala kwa madzi otentha kwambiri
  56,94,Ndi kulowetsedwa ku Gahena
  56,95,Ndithudi ichi ndi choonadi chosakayikitsa
  56,96,"Motero lemekezani dzina la Ambuye wanu, Wamkulu"
  57,1,"Chilichonse chimwe chili kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi chimalemekeza Mulungu. Iye ndiye Mwini mphamvu, Mwini nzeru"
  57,2,Wake ndi Ufumu wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi. Ndiye amene amapereka moyo ndi imfa ndipo ali ndi mphamvu pa zinthu zonse
  57,3,"Iye ndi woyamba ndi womaliza, wapamwamba mwamba ndi wapafupi. Ndipo Iye amadziwa zinthu zonse"
  57,4,"Ndiye adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi m’masiku asanu ndi limodzi ndipo adabuka pa mwamba pa mpando wake wa Chifumu. Iye amadziwa chilichonse chimene chimalowa m’nthaka ndi chilichonse chimene chimatuluka mu iyo, zonse zimene zimadza pansi kuchokera kumwamba ndi zonse zimene zimakwera kumwamba. Ndipo Iye ali nanu kulikonse kumene mungakhale. Ndipo Mulungu amaona zonse zimene mumachita"
  57,5,Wake ndi Ufumu wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi. Ndipo ndi kwa Iye kumene zonse zimabwerera
  57,6,Iye amapanga usiku kulumikizana ndi usana ndi kupanga usana kulumikizana ndi usiku. Iye amadziwa zinsinsi zonse zili m’mitima
  57,7,"Khulupirirani mwa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake. Perekani zopereka zaulere kuchokera ku zinthu zimene Mulungu wakupatsani kuti zikhale zanu. Iwo a inu amene akhulupilira ndipo apereka chaulere, yawo idzakhala mphotho yaikulu"
  57,8,"Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani kuti inu simukhulupirira mwa Mulungu? Pamene Mtumwi ali kukuitanani kuti mukhulupirire mwa Ambuye wanu ndipo Iye, ndithudi, walandira lonjezo lanu ngati inu ndinu anthu okhulupirira"
  57,9,"Ndiye amene amatumiza kwa kapolo wake zizindikiro zooneka kuti akhoza kukutsogolerani inu kuchoka ku mdima waukulu kupita kowala. Ndipo, ndithudi, Mulungu, kwa inuyo, ndi wachifundo ndi wachisoni"
  57,10,"Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani inu simufuna kupereka m’njira ya Mulungu? Mulungu ndiye Mwini wa zonse zili kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi. Palibe ofanana, pakati panu, ndi iwo amene amapereka chaulere ndipo adamenya nawo nkhondo poyamba kupambana kusanadze. Amenewa ndi a pamwamba kuposa iwo amene adapereka chaulere ndi kumenya nkhondo pambuyo pake. Koma kwa onsewa, Mulungu walonjeza mphotho yokoma. Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa zonse zimene mumachita"
  57,11,Kodi ndani amene adzakongoza Mulungu ngongole yabwino kuti Iye aipindulitse ndipo kuti iye adzakhale ndi mphotho ina yapamwamba
  57,12,"Patsiku limeneli inu mudzaona amuna okhulupirira ndi akazi okhulupirira, nyali zawo zili kuyaka patsogolo pawo ndi kudzanja lawo lamanja, kulonjerana kwawo kudzakhala nkhani yabwino kwa inu lero lino! Minda imene pansi pake pamayenda madzi mudzakhala m’menemo mpaka kalekale. Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwenikweni"
  57,13,"Patsiku limene amuna a chinyengo ndi akazi a chinyengo adzanena kwa iwo okhulupirira:“Tidikirirenikutitikhozakulandirachilangali kuchokera ku muuni wanu.” Koma kudzanenedwa kuti: “Bwererani m’mbuyo kuti mukafune muuni wanu. Ndipo chipupa chidzakhazikitsidwa pakati pawo chokhala ndi khomo. Mbali ina ya chipupachi kudzakhala chisomo pamene mbali ina kudzakhala chilango.”"
  57,14,"Iwo adzalira kwa iwo. “Kodi inu sitinali kukhalira limodzi?” Okhulupilira adzayankha kuti: “Zoonadi koma inu mudadzisocheretsa nokha. Inu mudanyengedwa, mudakayikira ndipo zilakolako zanu zidakunyengani inu mpaka pamene chilango cha Mulungu chinachitika. Ndipo wonyenga adakunyengani inu pa nkhani zokhudza Mulungu.”"
  57,15,"Motero lero palibe chiphuphu chimene chidzalandiridwa kuchokera kwa inu kapena iwo amene adakana Mulungu. Malo anu okhala ndi kumoto, amenewo ndiwo malo okhawo amene mudzalandiridwako ndipo ndi malo oipitsitsa kukhalamo"
  57,16,"Kodi nthawi siinakwane yoti okhulupirira enieni apereke mitima yawo modzichepetsa ndipo kuti azikumbukira Mulungu ndi choonadi chimene chavumbulutsidwa kwa iwo ndipo kuti asakhale ngati iwo amene adapatsidwa Buku nthawi ya kale? Koma patapita nthawi, mitima yawo idalimba. Ndipo ambiri a iwo ndi ophwanya malamulo"
  57,17,Dziwani kuti Mulungu amapereka moyo ku nthaka ikafa. Ndithudi taonetsa chivumbulutso chathu poyera kwa inu kuti mukhoza kuzindikira
  57,18,"Ndithudi iwo amene amapereka chopereka chaulere, amuna kapena akazi, iwo amasunga gawo lawo kwa Mulungu lomwe lidzaonjezeredwa mopitiriza muyeso ndipo adzakhala ndi mphotho yolemekezeka"
  57,19,"Ndipo iwo amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi mwa Mtumwi wake, iwo ndi olungama ndi okhulupirira pamaso pa Ambuye wawo. Iwo adzalandira mphotho yawo pamodzi ndi muuni. Ndipo iwo amene sakhulupirira ndipo amakana chivumbulutso chathu, amenewa ndiwo a ku moto wa ku Gahena"
  57,20,"Dziwani kuti moyo wa padziko lino lapansi ndi masewera ndi wotailako nthawi, chionetsero ndi kunyada ndi mpikisano pakati pa wina ndi mnzake wofuna chuma ndi ana. Fanizo lake lili ngati mvula ndi zomera zimene zimadza chifukwa cha zimene zimabweretsa chisangalalo kwa ozilima. Pasanapite nthawi izo zimafota ndi kuoneka za chikasu. Ndipo zimauma ndi kugwa pansi. Koma m’moyo umene uli kudza, kuli chilango chowawa kwa anthu ogona m’machimo ndi chikhululukiro chochokera kwa Mulungu ndiponso chisangalalo chake kwa iwo amene amadzipereka kwa Mulungu. Kodi moyo wa padziko lino lapansi ndi chiyani kupatula chinyengo chabe"
  57,21,Kotero fulumirani kupeza chikhululukiro cha Mulungu ndi munda wa Paradiso umene kutalika kwake kuli ngati kukula kwa kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi umene udakonzedwera iwo amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi Atumwi ake. Chimenechi ndicho chisomo cha Mulungu chimene amapereka kwa amene Iye wamufuna. Mulungu ndi Ambuye wa chisomo chosatha
  57,22,Palibe vuto limene limadza padziko kapena pa inu limene silinakhazikitsidwe kale Ife tisanalibweretse. Ndithudi chimenechi ndi chosavuta kwa Mulungu
  57,23,Kuti inu musakhumudwe chifukwa cha zinthu zabwino zimene simudazipeze kapena kunyada chifukwa cha zokoma zimene zaperekedwa kwa inu. Mulungu sakonda anthu odzikundikira
  57,24,"Ndiponso anthu a umbombo amauza anzawo kuti nawonso azikhala a umbombo. Ngati wina abwerera m’mbuyo kuchokera ku njira ya Mulungu, ndithudi, Mulungu sasowa chilichonse ndipo ndi wolemekezeka"
  57,25,Ndithudi tidatumiza kale Atumwi athu ndi zizindikiro zooneka ndipo tidatumiza pamodzi ndi iwo Buku ndi muyeso kuti anthu akhoza kukhala ndi makhalidwe abwino. Ndipo Ife tidapanga chitsulo chimene m’kati mwake muli mphamvu ndi zinthu zambiri zabwino kwa anthu. Kuti Mulungu akhoza kuyesa iwo amene amamuthandiza Iye ndi Mtumwi wake mwamseri. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wolimba ndi wamphamvu
  57,26,Ndithudi Ife tidatumiza Nowa ndi Abrahamu ndipo tidapereka kwa ana awo mphatso ya Utumwi ndi Buku ndipo ena pakati pawo ndi otsogozedwa bwino koma ambiri ndi ophwanya malamulo
  57,27,"Ndipo tidawapanga Atumwi athu kuti atsatire m’mapazi mwawo; Ndipo tidatumiza Yesu, mwana wa Maria, pambuyo pake ndipo tidamupatsa Uthenga wabwino. Ndipo tidaika m’mitima mwa iwo amene adali kumutsatira iye kukoma mtima ndi chisoni. Ukakhala unsembe iwo adapeka okha, chifukwa Ife sitidawalamulire kuti akhazikitse kupatula kuti azifunafuna chisangalalo cha Mulungu koma iwo sadazilabadire ayi. Kotero tidawapatsa mphotho iwo amene adakhulupirira koma ambiri a iwo ndi oswa malamulo"
  57,28,oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Samalani udindo wanu kwa Mulungu ndipo mukhulupilire mwa Mtumwi wake. Iye adzakupatsani magawo awiri a chisomo chake ndikukonzerani muuni umene muzidzayenda nawo ndi kukukhululukirani machimo anu. Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi wachisoni chosatha
  57,29,Kuti anthu a m’Buku adziwe kuti iwo alibe mphamvu ina iliyonse pa chisomo cha Mulungu ndipo kuti chisomo chake chili m’manja mwake mokha ndipo amachipereka kwa aliyense amene Iye wamufuna. Mulungu ndiye Mwini mphatso zosatha